lyrics:
[verse]
When the day is long and your heart feels heavy
Close your eyes and let it all unravel gently
In the midst of chaos, love will guide your way
Just surrender to the rhythm and find solace in its sway

[chorus]
Relax, my love, let the world melt away
In your tender embrace, all worries will fade
Let the melody of our hearts be our sanctuary
In this tranquil moment, love's sanctuary
